2788,IssuesEvent,2017-01-03 23:46:11+00:00,1938370,Mottie/tablesorter,24481435,rnesolydev,,,closed,Filter is not firing,"[{'id': 153147, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/Mottie/tablesorter/labels/How%20To...', 'name': 'How To...', 'color': 'fbca04', 'default': False}, {'id': 356453637, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/Mottie/tablesorter/labels/Themes', 'name': 'Themes', 'color': '0e8a16', 'default': False}, {'id': 30749346, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/Mottie/tablesorter/labels/Widget', 'name': 'Widget', 'color': '207de5', 'default': False}, {'id': 224191957, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/Mottie/tablesorter/labels/Widget-Filter', 'name': 'Widget-Filter', 'color': '207de5', 'default': False}]",[],10,"I have been using the table sorter and I am now trying to add the Filter option.  The filter box is coming up, but no filtering is taking place.  I am sure its just that I am missing something but I can not figure out what I forgot to add.

I am using version 2.28.3 of the tablesorter.js.

I added the widgetoptions property, the filter to the headers property,  and added filter to the widgets property.  The javascript looks like this …

 ```
$(""#<% =gvContractors.ClientID %>"").tablesorter({
                showProcessing: true,
                sortList: [[1, 0], [2, 0]],
                headers: { 0: { sorter: false, filter: false} },
                widgets: [""zebra"", ""filter""],
                widgetOptions: {
                    filter_liveSearch: true,
                    filter_columnFilters: true,
                    filter_reset: '.reset'
                }
            })
```

Here is the css that I added ...


```
/* filter row */
.tablesorter-filter-row td {
  background: #ffe7c6;
  line-height: normal;
  text-align: center; /* center the input */
  -webkit-transition: line-height 0.1s ease;
  -moz-transition: line-height 0.1s ease;
  -o-transition: line-height 0.1s ease;
  transition: line-height 0.1s ease;
}
/* optional disabled input styling */
.tablesorter-filter-row .disabled {
  opacity: 0.5;
  filter: alpha(opacity=50);
  cursor: not-allowed;
  background: #ffe7c6;
  border-style : none;
}

/* hidden filter row */
.tablesorter-filter-row.hideme td {
  /*** *********************************************** ***/
  /*** change this padding to modify the thickness     ***/
  /*** of the closed filter row (height = padding x 2) ***/
  padding: 2px;
  /*** *********************************************** ***/
  margin: 0;
  line-height: 0;
  cursor: pointer;
}
.tablesorter-filter-row.hideme .tablesorter-filter {
  height: 1px;
  min-height: 0;
  border: 0;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0;
  /* don't use visibility: hidden because it disables tabbing */
  opacity: 0;
  filter: alpha(opacity=0);
}

/* filters */
.tablesorter-filter {
  width: 95%;
  height: inherit;
  margin: 4px;
  padding: 4px;
  background-color: #fff;
  border: 1px solid #bbb;
  color: #333;
  -webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
