3883,IssuesEvent,2017-05-02 06:07:14+00:00,11379148,jasonish/py-idstools,644115,jasonish,,,closed,Improvement: rulecat report only if needed,[],[],1,"Rulecat script when using the option `--merged` always generate a report [as you can see in the code](https://github.com/jasonish/py-idstools/blob/master/idstools/scripts/rulecat.py#L416), WHICH is logged with level `INFO`.

