8113,IssuesEvent,2015-08-06 22:55:26+00:00,24774658,boto/boto3,521949,alangarf,327752,boto,opened,Add resource waiters to IAM resources,[],[],0,"Need to add waiters for the IAM policy, role and instance-profile creation because if you try launching an instance with the returned values of the create_instance_profile call you can get this.

