9688,IssuesEvent,2017-01-12 21:44:53+00:00,15958352,GetBlimp/django-rest-framework-jwt,15911477,Chuck-Aguilar,1227237,GetBlimp,opened,Token Questions,[],[],0,"HI!
I really appreciate jwt. 

I just wanna know a few things. 

