11235,IssuesEvent,2018-08-09 18:31:20+00:00,16316451,GoogleCloudPlatform/google-cloud-python,1022400,DazWilkin,2810941,GoogleCloudPlatform,opened,Container: example(s) for long-running operations,[],[],0,"Please provide (reference) an example for converting `container_v1.types.Operation` into `api_core.operatoin.Operation`.

[`create_cluster`](https://googlecloudplatform.github.io/google-cloud-python/latest/_modules/google/cloud/container_v1/gapic/cluster_manager_client.html#ClusterManagerClient.create_cluster) (and other methods in the Cloud Client Library) return (long-running) `Operation`(s).

I assumed (hoped) this would be `google.api_core.operation.Operation` that I could `operation.result()` but, the method turns [`google.cloud.container_v1.types.Operation`](https://googlecloudplatform.github.io/google-cloud-python/latest/container/gapic/v1/types.html#google.cloud.container_v1.types.Operation)

[Spanner's Python Library, for example, [returns](https://googlecloudplatform.github.io/google-cloud-python/latest/spanner/instance-api.html#google.cloud.spanner_v1.instance.Instance.create) google.api_core.operation.Operation in this case]

I'm struggling to connect this with (presumably?) [Long-Running Operations](https://googlecloudplatform.github.io/google-cloud-python/latest/core/operation.html) documented in Core.

I'm unable to new an `OperationsClient`. The Example suggests `operations_v1.OperationsClient()` but this errors with `TypeError: __init__() takes at least 2 arguments (1 given).`

It's unclear what `channel (grpc.Channel)` I should provide.

Is this the correct approach? Having triggered the cluster creation, I'd like to track its progress to completion.",{},{}
11240,IssuesEvent,2017-04-26 09:51:50+00:00,16316451,GoogleCloudPlatform/google-cloud-python,9477296,kosmiciatakuja,2810941,GoogleCloudPlatform,opened,speech_contexts parameter of Sample.long_running_recognize() limited to 50 phrases?,[],[],0,"The `speech_contexts` parameter to `long_running_recognize` method of the Sample has a description that starts with: 

