11285,IssuesEvent,2018-06-27 22:02:06+00:00,16316451,GoogleCloudPlatform/google-cloud-python,242750,tseaver,2810941,GoogleCloudPlatform,closed,"Documentation Unclear: ""If the property is not set locally, returns None.""","[{'id': 958354227, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWw5NTgzNTQyMjc=', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/GoogleCloudPlatform/google-cloud-python/labels/:rotating_light:', 'name': ':rotating_light:', 'color': 'FFFFFF', 'default': False}, {'id': 77678602, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWw3NzY3ODYwMg==', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/GoogleCloudPlatform/google-cloud-python/labels/api:%20storage', 'name': 'api: storage', 'color': 'f8f8f8', 'default': False}, {'id': 77676134, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWw3NzY3NjEzNA==', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/GoogleCloudPlatform/google-cloud-python/labels/documentation', 'name': 'documentation', 'color': 'bfdadc', 'default': False}, {'id': 544604243, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWw1NDQ2MDQyNDM=', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/GoogleCloudPlatform/google-cloud-python/labels/priority:%20p2', 'name': 'priority: p2', 'color': 'fef2c0', 'default': False}, {'id': 744431537, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWw3NDQ0MzE1Mzc=', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/GoogleCloudPlatform/google-cloud-python/labels/type:%20process', 'name': 'type: process', 'color': 'c5def5', 'default': False}]","[{'login': 'tseaver', 'id': 242750, 'node_id': 'MDQ6VXNlcjI0Mjc1MA==', 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/242750?v=4', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tseaver', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/tseaver', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tseaver/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tseaver/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tseaver/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tseaver/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tseaver/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tseaver/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tseaver/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tseaver/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tseaver/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",5,"The [Google Storage Blob documentation](https://googlecloudplatform.github.io/google-cloud-python/latest/storage/blobs.html) says that almost all properties return the value `None` if the ""property is not set locally."" However, there is no documentation explaining how properties are set/unset locally or when that occurs. 

This is confusing, there should be a preamble explaining when local Blob properties are set locally.

### Motivation

I ran into this because I started seeing some of these values return `None` in my project in unexpected circumstances (there may be another bug there), but when I went to the documentation, it did not shed much light on why or when these properties should be returning `None`.",{},{}
