11532,IssuesEvent,2017-09-03 08:49:34+00:00,4086616,shadowsocks/shadowsocks,535565,sorz,3006190,shadowsocks,opened,Consider making a new release (v3.0.0?),[],[],0,"Current lastest version 2.9.1 was released in 8 months ago.
It's too old. Critical features like AEAD are missing.

Although users who follow the readme are able to install the latest one directly from git,
downstream packaging, like [Arch Linux's](https://www.archlinux.org/packages/community/any/shadowsocks/), rely on version tags on this git repo.

Please tag a new version number to allow downstream packages to catch up.

Thanks.",{},{}
