11801,IssuesEvent,2017-06-06 15:32:44+00:00,75023443,awslabs/aws-cfn-template-flip,111803,charltones,3299148,awslabs,opened,Escaped newlines in json result in de-escaped newlines in yml,[],[],0,"For example:

