12394,IssuesEvent,2016-02-16 03:14:14+00:00,10247874,docker/docker-py,555156,achimnol,5429470,docker,opened,Hostconfig doc should link the available list of ulimit names,[],[],0,"Currently, [the doc about hostconfig](https://docker-py.readthedocs.org/en/latest/hostconfig/) does not state what option names are available for ulimits parameter, such as `nproc`, `nofile`. The exact list for this parameter is defined by [docker/go-units](https://github.com/docker/go-units) subproject of docker, as in [ulimit.go#L46](https://github.com/docker/go-units/blob/master/ulimit.go#L46).
Although the ""shorthand"" name of ulimit options might be a ""common sense"" knowledge for system engineers, I think it would be better to provide the exact list of options for each configuration parameter whenever possible.",{},{}
