13153,IssuesEvent,2018-01-08 18:39:30+00:00,6235174,conda/conda,391586,pvanderlinden,6392739,conda,opened,Bogus ResolvePackageNotFound,[],[],0,"I'm trying to install a package from our internal conda channel, but since 4.4 conda fails to do this if you do it with an environment file, and I'm not sure what causes this. Downgrading conda solves the issue, but brings other issues.

