13930,IssuesEvent,2017-10-05 15:32:47+00:00,33653601,jupyter/notebook,11225150,miquelmarti,7388996,jupyter,opened,Missing import names in notebook,[],[],0,"While I can do `from mymodule import MyClass` in the IPython terminal, I cannot do it in the notebook.

