15483,IssuesEvent,2016-11-09 23:50:25+00:00,597114,Becksteinlab/GromacsWrapper,6104558,mohebifar,11325701,Becksteinlab,opened,Invalid conversion specification when doing itp.write,[],[],0,"I have this piece of code for reading an ITP file, modifying it and writing a new one. I have taken out the modification part because it doesn't work anyway:

```python
