15774,IssuesEvent,2017-09-16 01:00:56+00:00,6704888,django-import-export/django-import-export,9125193,juliocebrito,12345453,django-import-export,opened,"Help with override save_instance, i need compare old value and new value for field ""concepto_ni""",[],[],0,"def save_instance(self, instance, using_transactions=True, dry_run=False):

