15848,IssuesEvent,2016-12-11 15:26:57+00:00,37496521,nteract/nteract,5368903,jkornblum,12401040,nteract,opened,Unexpected statusbar update behavior,[],[],0,"When I run code the status bar changes to ""python3 | idle"" to ""python3 | busy"" as expected.
