18408,IssuesEvent,2018-06-11 16:23:06+00:00,87358890,KrishnaswamyLab/PHATE,32019333,tarak77,26941417,KrishnaswamyLab,opened,PHATE for single cell HiC data?,[],[],0,"Hello,
Compared to population based HiC data, single cell HiC data are very sparse and hence good imputation methods are needed to fill in the contact matrix. 
