18544,IssuesEvent,2018-03-21 18:30:45+00:00,102692863,onnx/onnx,36478,dougalsutherland,31675368,onnx,opened,pypi version requires protobuf 3.4,[],[],0,"Because `sdist` includes `onnx.pb.h`, the generated source distribution can only be used with the same(ish) version of `protobuf` as whoever generated the source. Particularly, `pip install onnx` doesn't work right now if you have protobuf 3.5.

Since you need protobuf at compile time anyway, it'd probably be better to change `setup.py` to not include these files in `sdist`s but generate them at compile time instead....",{},{}
